&lt;p&gt;Our mission is to improve the lives of people and communities by democratizing technology development in health and research.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Senior Platform Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
