&lt;p&gt;We’re building a next-generation Healthcare App Platform — a flexible foundation that enables rapid development of high-quality, customizable healthcare applications. This is not your typical role — we’re building the platform that builds the products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthcare apps share a lot of the same DNA — appointments, care plans, status tracking, forms, communication, reporting. The challenge is in allowing for workflow customization without sacrificing developer productivity or runtime performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for Senior Engineers to help define and build the service-oriented architecture that powers this platform, in collaboration with in-house SMEs, product, and design partners.&lt;/p&gt;
