&lt;li&gt;Designing and building core platform services in Node.js / NestJS, focused on performance, modularity, and long-term maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modeling complex domains in PostgreSQL, using sound data architecture principles (BCNF/3NF) to power customizable healthcare workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating internal tooling, APIs, and libraries that accelerate product teams and enable safe, scalable customization across applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating across product, design, and clinical teams to shape platform capabilities that directly support real-world healthcare use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enabling front-end teams to build high-quality applications by providing reliable, well-documented service interfaces and reusable UI primitives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balancing short-term delivery with long-term vision, making tradeoffs explicit and optimizing for developer velocity, product agility, and platform consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving platform adoption by aligning evolution of internal tools with the needs of product and solution delivery teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
