&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chorus Innovations is a fast-growing healthcare technology company with an adaptive platform as a service (PaaS) that enables the rapid development of mobile, desktop, text messaging and interactive voice applications. Chorus’ platform currently powers transformative healthcare, biomedical research and community health projects across institutions and public health agencies nationwide. We believe every community should have world-class health technology so they can thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission is to improve the lives of people and communities by democratizing technology development in health and research.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chorus is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;VP of Product Management &lt;/strong&gt;to define, build, and lead our Product Management function through the next stage of our platform evolution and product strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a transformative executive who will not only drive our product strategy but will actively shape the culture, talent, and operational rigor of the product organization. The right candidate will define what high quality product management looks like at Chorus, establishing clear ownership, high standards of accountability, and modern product practices. This person will recruit, mentor, and elevate a team of product managers, empowering them to operate with autonomy and clear alignment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with Engineering, Design, Clinical Solutions, and Go-To-Market teams, this person will translate market signals into scalable, AI-enabled products while fostering a highly collaborative, cross-functional product culture. Ultimately, this leader will drive Chorus’s transition from custom, project-based delivery toward a scalable, market-ready product organization.&lt;/p&gt;
