&lt;li&gt;Define and lead product strategy across Chorus’s platform, product lines, reusable templates, and application capabilities, aligning them directly with overall company goals. Empower and guide a team of Product Managers to translate this high-level strategy into actionable, high-impact product roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish the frameworks for roadmap development and prioritization, balancing customer needs, Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) fit, market opportunity, business value, engineering feasibility, and delivery commitments. Hold the product team accountable for data-driven prioritization decisions and measurable product outcomes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
