&lt;li&gt;Build clear executive and leadership visibility into roadmap priorities, product readiness, tradeoffs, dependencies, and key decisions, serving as the primary champion and communicator of Chorus&#39;s product vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
